360 PHOTO ALERT - Google "I/O" is Google's annual developer conference and technology expo.  In years past it has been held in downtown San Francisco, CA but this year, Google moved the event closer to it's Mountain View headquarters, to the Shoreline Amphitheatre.

This 360 showcases the main art installation of the I/O "sign" which served as the gateway into Google's technological playground this year! Enjoy the California sunshine as you spin this 360 photo around!

Des

posts.text:
This past week I spent a bit of time explaining the mechanics of Speed/Power. The good thing about teaching a seasoned group, is that we can go deep into the concepts. This changes how they experience the art of Serrada and infuses their other arts with greater depth also. Here is a 10 minute clip from the lessons.

Serrada's speed/power is legendary (Manong Angel frequently said "three strikes and a man will fall." ) I am now pushing the Bay Area Group to develop their speed - not empty speed but speed that also is Packing (an internal arts reference, think of it as hitting with spirit/intent).

If packing speed/power development is important to you, come join us in the Bay Area. All styles/systems welcome, bring a willing heart, check your ego at the gate and let us grow together.

Signing off from Ground Zero of Serrada. Stockton. @[100011519460918:2048:Ron] @[100008895422325:2048:Saturno]

#RonSaturno #CabalesSerradaEskrima #Serrada #ModernSerrada #Stockton #MountainView #BayAreaGroup #AngelCaballes #Manong

Immaculate 3 bedroom/2 bathroom home built for entertaining! The open concept living/kitchen/dining room area boasts 15' ceilings and is filled with natural light. Property includes energy efficient radiant heat floors throughout as well as central air conditioning. Two over-sized garage bays are underneath with ample room for a workbench. Two expansive decks on either side of house provide for abundant outdoor entertaining space and mountain views. Situated in low-tax Tuftonboro in the Hidden Valley Association, you have two association beaches on idyllic Lower Beach Pond and association tennis courts for your enjoyment.
